casebody.data:
HOME DESIGN SERVICES, INC., petitioner,
v.
TURNER HERITAGE HOMES INC., et al. No. 16-858. Supreme Court of the United States March 20, 2017.

Motion of The American Institute of Building Design, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
